en.name: M249 5.56x45 Light Machinegun
en.description: The M249 SAW (Squad Automatic Weapon) is a gas operated and air cooled light machinegun widely used by the U.S. Armed Forces. The weapon was introduced in 1984 to address a lack of sustained automatic fire capability at the squad level. The M249 SAW combines the rate of fire of a machine gun with the accuracy and portability of an assault rifle.
